n, accounting, behavioral finance, Second Life, serious games</font></p></center><p><font size="2" FACE="Myriad Roman, Arial, Helvetica, Sans-serif;"><b>JEL Classifications:</b> A10, A20, C88, C90, D00, E00, G00, M00, P00</font></p></center><font size = "2" FACE="Myriad Roman, Arial, Helvetica, Sans-serif;">Working Paper Series</font></div><h4 style="margin-left: 15px;">						Date posted: <font style="font-weight:normal">May 25, 2007</font>; Last revised: <font style="font-weight:normal">October 12, 2009</font></h4><div id="suggestedCitation" class="regtext11"><h4 style="margin-left: 15px; !important; font-weight: bold !important;">Suggested Citation</h4><p style="margin-left: 15px !important; margin-right: 10px !important;" class="regtext11"><div class="simField" style="text-decoration:none;font-size:11px;overflow: hidden;	margin-left: 15px;width: 544px;" >Bloomfield, Robert  J., Worlds for Study: Invitation - Virtual Worlds for Studying Real-World Business (and Law, and Politics, and Sociology, and....) (May 25, 2007).  Available at SSRN: http://ssrn.com/abstract=988984</div></p><BLOCKQUOTE><form name="frmExport"><br><FONT size="2" FACE="Myriad Roman, Arial, Helvetica, Sans-serif;">Export to:<select name="cboFormat" style="text-decoration:none;" ><option value="2" >BibTeX</option><option value="1" selected>EndNote</option><option value="3" >RefMan</option><option value="4" >RefWorks</option></select>    <span class="purpleBTN"><a href="#" onClick="location.href='RefExport.cfm?abstract_id=988984&format=' + document.frmExport.cboFormat.value;">Export Citation</a></span><a style="font-size:9px; padding-top: 10px;" class="textlink" href="#" onClick="window.open('RefExport.cfm?function=info&abstract_id=988984&format=' + document.frmExport.cboFormat.value,'Info','toolbar=no,menubar=no,scrollbars=yes,resizable=yes,width=670,height=450');">What's this?</a> </FONT></form></BLOCKQUOTE></div><div id="ContactInfo"><h4 style="margin-left: 15px